BT /F2 11 Tf 50 675 Td (1. Purpose & Scope) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 50 657 Td (This document defines the end-to-end incident management lifecycle for the Safaricom Ethiopia) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 50 644 Td (Network Operations Center \(NOC\). It governs all network events from initial alarm detection) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 50 631 Td (through resolution, closure, and post-incident review.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 50 610 Td (2. Severity Classification) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 592 Td (• P1 \(Critical\): Total service outage affecting >10,000 subscribers. MTTR target: 4 hours.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 579 Td (• P2 \(High\): Partial outage or >30% degradation. MTTR target: 5 hours.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 566 Td (• P3 \(Medium\): Single-site or isolated degradation. MTTR target: 8 hours.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 553 Td (• P4 \(Low\): Minor performance deviation, no subscriber impact. MTTR target: 12 hours.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 50 532 Td (3. Detection & Triage \(L1 NOC\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 514 Td (• Monitor OSS/NMS dashboards continuously across all 7 regions.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 501 Td (• Log alarm in ticketing system within 5 minutes of detection.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 488 Td (• Assign severity level per classification table above.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 475 Td (• Initiate MTCT \(Mean Time to Call Team\) clock immediately.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 50 454 Td (4. Escalation Pathway) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 436 Td (• P1/P2: Immediate escalation to L2 Domain Engineer on duty.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 423 Td (• P3/P4: L1 attempts resolution; escalate after MTCW threshold exceeded.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 410 Td (• L2 Domain Engineer engages L3 Vendor Support for unresolved P1/P2.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 397 Td (• Management notification mandatory for all P1 incidents within 15 minutes.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 50 376 Td (5. Resolution & Closure) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 358 Td (• Verify full service restoration before closing ticket.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 345 Td (• Document root cause, resolution steps, and elapsed time.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 332 Td (• Complete post-incident report \(PIR\) within 24 hours for P1/P2.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 319 Td (• Conduct Lessons Learned session within 48 hours of P1 closure.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 50 298 Td (6. SLA Performance Targets) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 280 Td (• MTCT \(Mean Time to Call Team\) — P1: 15 min, P2: 20 min.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 267 Td (• MTCW \(Mean Time to Clear Warning\) — P1: 30 min, P2: 45 min.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 254 Td (• MTTR \(Mean Time to Repair\) — P1: 240 min, P2: 300 min.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 50 30 Td (CONFIDENTIAL — For internal NOC use only. Safaricom Ethiopia PLC.) Tj ET
